Pfc. Sabrina Vimoto, left, 7th Group Special Forces Group, stands with her father, Command Sgt. Maj. Isaia Vimoto, 173rd Airborne at her Basic Combat Training graduation at Fort Jackson, S.C., Oct. 30, 2013. Sabrina Vimoto reflected on her heritage, her experience as an Army brat, the tragedy of losing a sibling in combat and as a Soldier who served under her fatherâ€™s leadership. (Courtesy photo)
